  "closure_text": "V6r baseline (no intra-Class-2 dynamics) = 3.55e-05; V1 empirical level = 4.56e-04. The Sec 14.6.2 intra-Class-2 technological-exp axiom yields V7 = V6r * exp((t-t_intel_cosmic)/tau_tech). Kardashev-band tau_tech in [1, 2] Gyr gives |Dw(z=0.28)| in [1.47e-05, 2.48e-05] (Kardashev-band envelope). V1's empirical level matches V7 at tau_tech = 10.00 Gyr -- OUTSIDE the physically-anchored Kardashev band. The principled load-bearing closure of O.13 under the combined Class-2 axiom (Sec 14.5.2) + technological-exp axiom (Sec 14.6.2) is the Kardashev-band envelope; the pre-F-prime V6r-to-V1 envelope (13x width) is narrowed to 2x in the principled band."
